# DeepSeek-V4 indexer + MoE trace instrumentation for antirez/ds4
# Upstream: https://github.com/antirez/ds4  commit 80ebbc396aee40eedc1d829222f3362d10fa4c6c (MIT)
# Apply from the ds4 repo root:  git apply ds4_instrumentation.patch  (or: patch -p1 < ...)
# Adds env-gated JSONL logging of (a) CSA indexer top-k KV selections (DS4_TRACE_*) and
# (b) MoE routed-expert top-6 selections (DS4_MOE_TRACE=1 -> <DS4_TRACE_OUTPUT>/moe_trace.jsonl).
# Build: make cpu
# ---
